About Senate Committee on Rules and Administration

About Senate Committee on Rules and Administration

The jurisdiction of the Senate Committee on Rules and Administration is specified in Rule XXV, Clause 1 of the Senate Manual. Visit the committee's website for more information including membership and rules.

The publications on this page are available at the committee's discretion. A "No results found" message below means there are currently no applicable publications in the system.
